title: Bobby’s Super Bowl Chicken Wings Fiasco…Why He Had to Calm Down A Hostile Crowd + Name the Country Artist Wishing You A Happy Valentine’s Day + Suzy Bogguss her 90’s Country Hit and shares stories about Garth Brooks & Dolly Parton!
itunes:title: Bobby’s Super Bowl Chicken Wings Fiasco…Why He Had to Calm Down A Hostile Crowd + Name the Country Artist Wishing You A Happy Valentine’s Day + Suzy Bogguss her 90’s Country Hit and shares stories about Garth Brooks & Dolly Parton!
description:
We recap the best moments from the Super Bowl and why Bobby thought the halftime show was the best of all-time. Bobby shares a crazy story that happened when he went to pick up chicken wings for his small Super Bowl party. We celebrate Valentine’s Day by seeing if we can guess the country artist wishing you a Happy Valentine’s Day.
